About
  node-auto is a bash script providing fast, automated, stainless way to install node without interfering with any choice.
  It installs node locally for you, and npm as well, except for a customized location is specified.
  sudo free.
  All you need to do is to install packages you want to use for your projects.

Usage:
  git clone https://github.com/calidion/node-auto.git
  sh node-auto.sh [version] [location]

  version can be customized, default now is v0.10.6
  location can also be customized if version is provided
